metadata.name: Doodle & Daisy
metadata.description:
This piece was inspired by looking around while I was sick and the doctor told me something.,

   Sometimes when I think about that one day we all will pass this earth. At the same time, I feel lonely thinking about that.

But if that day has come in someday, I just hope that I can meet my doodle punk frens in daisy meadow again..❤️

Created: Oct 30, 2022
